@startuml
participant "Nhan vien thu ngan" as NV
participant "May doc ma vach" as BarcodeReader
participant "May tinh" as PC
participant "May POS" as POS

NV -> BarcodeReader: Quet ma san pham
BarcodeReader -> PC: Gui du lieu san pham
PC -> NV: Hien thi thong tin san pham va tinh tong tien
NV -> PC: Xac nhan thanh toan

alt Thanh toan bang the
    NV -> POS: Quet the thanh toan
    POS -> PC: Gui yeu cau xac nhan giao dich
    PC -> POS: Xac nhan giao dich
    POS -> NV: Thanh toan thanh cong
end

PC -> NV: In hoa don
NV -> PC: Dua hoa don va san pham
@enduml
